  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/20/allcast-receiver/\"><img alt=\"AllCast icon for Android\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/2b0724509557f2c052971c88c3afcb37/200136410/allcast-icon.jpg\" style=\"width: 620px; height: 339px;\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n由 Koushik Dutta 所制作的 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/tag/allcast\">AllCast</a> 应用基本上适用于所有机顶盒，但在之前的版本中，其串流功能在大多数 Android 设备上是无法实现的。不过从今天开始，情况就不同了。Dutta 已经专门推出了全新的 AllCast Receiver，让 Android 设备也可以被当作串流接收端来播放媒体内容了。除此之外，AllCast 本身也有更新，新版本可以将 Google Play Music 串流至其它硬件（需 root），有需要的朋友可以去升级试试喔。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/05/19/allcast-receiver/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"https://plus.google.com/u/0/110558071969009568835/posts/FwWk36Jt9yZ\" target=\"_blank\">Koushik Dutta (G+)</a></span>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.droid-life.com/2014/05/19/allcast-receiver-app-lets-you-stream-music-pictures-and-video-to-any-android-device/\" target=\"_blank\">Droid-Life</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.koushikdutta.cast.receiver\" target=\"_blank\">Google Play (AllCast Receiver)</a>、<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.koushikdutta.cast\" target=\"_blank\">(AllCast)</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/20/allcast-receiver/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20888688/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/20/allcast-receiver/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
